[div class=p 
	"The movie is well optimized and pretty entertaining. As such, it easily satisfies the criteria for acceptability. However, the use of a savegame start sparked a 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=discussion|href=/Forum/Topics/23493)
	" about savegame-start movies. Specifically for this submission, it was relevant to discuss whether a faster savegame-start movie could obsolete a clean start movie. In the end, it was 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=decided|href=/Forum/Posts/529407)
	" that savegame-start submissions can be accepted into a separate category, if they are faster than the normal start ones. 
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
